N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 191.1 - Eggs unfit for human food

State Regulations

Loss and inedible eggs shall be determined to be unfit for
human food and shall not be sold, offered for sale, or exposed for sale for
human food. Notes
